item.title: My Bucket List
item.description: I’m a big fan of lists, checklists, and to-do lists. It’s only natural that the idea of a “bucket list” is something that I am a fan of. Here is mine (I will probably update it frequently so feel free to check back from time to time): First IRL/non-Internet friend. First kiss. First relationship. Own a Tesla. Visit all 48 of the Continental United States. (maybe on a road trip?
